<h5>Useful Heroku commands</h5>
<p><b>run a rake task</b><br>
heroku rake convert:refresh_on_request --app her17
</p>

<p><b>Install Sendgrid Mailer</b><br>
heroku addons:create sendgrid:starter
</p>
<p><b>Install and open the scheduler</b><br>
heroku addons:create scheduler:standard<br>
heroku addons:open scheduler</p>
<p>
<p><b>monitor an app log</b><br>
heroku logs --tail --app heraga
</p>
<p><b>run rails console</b><br>
heroku run console --app heraga
</p>
<p><b>get info on app</b><br>
heroku info heraga
</p>
<hr>

<h5>Create a clone of a Heroku App</h5>
<a href='https://github.com/heroku/heroku-fork'>https://github.com/heroku/heroku-fork</a><br>
<p><b>install fork</b><br>
heroku plugins:install heroku-fork
</p>
<p><b>add the git repo</b><br>  
git remote add forked git@heroku.com:heraga.git
</p>
<p><b>create the new app</b><br>
heroku fork --from her17  --to heraga
</p>  
<p><b>push new code to apps</b><br>
git push forked master<br>
git push heroku master
</p>
