<h5>Using Ironstore cache on Heroku</h5>
<p><b>setup the ironcache store</b><br>
ironcache = IronCache::Client.new<br>
@cache = ironcache.cache("my_cache")<br>
@cache.put("poll_request", 'false')<br>
@cache.put("poll_request_time", Time.now.to_s)
</p>
